8 copie etc.: copying in their garret.

9 à grand eau: swilling the floors.

10 désinvolture: uninhibitedness.

11 vibgyor: violet-indigo-blue-green-yellow-orange-red.

12 sans façons: unceremoniously.

13 strapontin: folding seat in front.

14 décharné: emaciated.

15 cabane: hut.

16 allons donc: oh, come.

17 pointe assassine: the point (of a story or poem) that murders artistic merit.

